text:
Tough time to be a Chipotle lover. They just can't catch a break.

Last year was the E. coli and Salmonella outbreaks. This year? A major earnings miss last month,...

$CMG stock has plummeted over 45% since November 😮‍♂️ And now? Employees at multiple locations across Florida are testing positive for COVID-19 🤕

What do you think, traders? Time to buy the dip or wait for more bad news?

💼 $cmg daily

📊 Revenue: -0.47%
💸 Earnings Per Share:  $0.38 vs $0.94 est.

😬 $CMG is DOWN almost -6% after market close. Time for some nachos 😳 Anyone else sensing bargain opportunity 💸?"

* Traded volume of CMG stock on 02/06 is more than 4x the typical trading volume. It's clear investors think either $30+ is overvalued 📊 Or they're hoping for an upswing

### [04/27/20]

"Who needs free guac when the whole brand takes a dive downhill?

Investors sent $CMG into free fall today 🔴 Down nearly 15%! 💔

Why did Wall St have it in for CMG today?
